========================
phpGitAdmin Installation
========================



Apache Virtual host settings
----------------------------
<VirtualHost *:80>
   DocumentRoot "/path/to/our/phpgitadmin/public"
   ServerName www.phpgitadmin.dev
   ServerAlias phpgitadmin.dev

   # This should be omitted in the production environment
   SetEnv APPLICATION_ENV development

   <Directory "/path/to/our/phpgitadmin/public">
       Options MultiViews FollowSymLinks
       AllowOverride All
       Order allow,deny
       Allow from all
   </Directory>
</VirtualHost>



/etc/hosts
----------
127.0.0.1	www.phpgitadmin.dev phpgitadmin.dev



Aditional downloads
-------------------

Download Zend Framework 2 from:
http://framework.zend.com/

Download Doctrine Object Relational Mapper 2.1 from:
http://www.doctrine-project.org/

